                <p>The Old City (İçərişəhər) is an ancient residential quarter - historical and architectural reserve in the capital of Azerbaijan, Baku. Surrounded by well-preserved fortress walls, it is the most ancient part and landmark of the city. The most significant architectural monuments in Icheri-sheher are the Maiden Tower and the complex of Shirvanshahs Palace. Dozens of historical monuments are located here.</p>
